                </div>
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <p class="text-justify">The customer is required to register and log i to the site before any actions can be accessed. The customer can view parcels by using the link in the navigation bar. The customer can add parcels that will be delivered to themselves. The customer can browse all parcels that have been added to their delivery list and track an individual parcel. The tracking represents a list of updates that the ABCLogistics staff members have added in order to keep the customer updated with logistical progress.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
