                    <h4 class="text-center">Staff</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <p class="text-justify">The staff member is required to register and log in to the site before any actions can be accessed. The website administrator is required to give staff member the system role permissions of Staff. Staff members can view all the parcels in the database, they also have permission to create, edit and delete all parcels. A staff member is responsible for adding tracking information to a parcel which will be visible to customer associated with the order. Staff members can also update or delete tracking information.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="text-center">Admin</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <p class="text-justify">The website admin is required to register and log in to the site before any actions can be accessed. The admin does not have any permission limitations. Admins can view all of the register users of the site. Admins can also view and increase user permissions of the site. The admin can create, read, update and delete all system roles and also branches that are available for parcels to be dropped to.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
